Package neureka.devices.file.heads

Class IDXHead

java.lang.Object
neureka.devices.file.heads.AbstractFileHead<IDXHead,​java.lang.Number>
neureka.devices.file.heads.IDXHead
All Implemented Interfaces:
FileHead<IDXHead,​java.lang.Number>, Storage<java.lang.Number>
public class IDXHead
extends AbstractFileHead<IDXHead,​java.lang.Number>
This class is one of many extensions of the AbstractFileHead which is therefore ultimately an implementation of the FileHead interface. Like other FileHead implementations this class represents a file of a given type, in this case it represents a IDX file.

    • getDataSize

      public int getDataSize()
      Description copied from interface: FileHead
      This method returns the byte size of the data which is stored in the tensor of the file which is managed by this FileHead. The underlying datatype of the data within the file does not matter.
      Returns:
      The byte size of the data of the underlying tensor body.

    • getTotalSize

      public int getTotalSize()
      Description copied from interface: FileHead
      This method returns the number of bytes which are used to store the tensor in the file whose access is being managed by an implementation of th FileHead interface. Meta data stored inside the file will also be included in this returned size.
      Returns:
      The byte size of all the bytes used to represent the tensor in the file.
